carat-open(1) -- Opens the source directory for a gem in your carat
=====================================================================

## SYNOPSIS

`carat open` [GEM]

## DESCRIPTION

Opens the source directory of the provided GEM in your editor.

For this to work the `EDITOR` or `CARAT_EDITOR` environment variable has to
be set.

Example:

    carat open 'rack'

Will open the source directory for the 'rack' gem in your carat.
